---
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Digital Impact GPT</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
background:black;
color:white;
}

.hero{
height:100vh;
background:url("/hero.jpg") center/cover no-repeat;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
text-align:center;
}

.hero-overlay{
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
padding:60px;
border-radius:20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:60px;
letter-spacing:4px;
margin:0;
}

.hero p{
font-size:20px;
opacity:0.9;
margin-top:20px;
}

.section{
padding:100px 20px;
max-width:1200px;
margin:auto;
text-align:center;
}

.cards{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:40px;
margin-top:60px;
}

.card{
background:#0b0f1a;
padding:30px;
border-radius:12px;
border:1px solid #1f2a44;
}

.card h3{
color:#ffd36a;
}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:40px;
opacity:0.6;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-overlay">

<h1>DIGITAL IMPACT GPT</h1>

<p>
Enterprise AI Intelligence Platform
</p>

<p>
Transform complex data into strategic intelligence
</p>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<h2>Core Capabilities</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>AI Automation</h3>
<p>
Automates complex workflows and analytical processes using intelligent orchestration.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Data Intelligence</h3>
<p>
Processes and analyzes large-scale structured and unstructured data in real time.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Neural Systems</h3>
<p>
Self-learning architectures capable of adapting to dynamic data environments.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<h2>Technology Stack</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>Python AI Infrastructure</h3>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Pandas / NumPy</h3>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Neural Network Models</h3>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Distributed Cloud Computing</h3>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

Digital Impact GPT © 2026

</footer>

</body>
</html>
